that time of year.

00:05:57.691 --> 00:05:58.983 position:50% align:center
Oh, yeah, it sure is.

00:05:59.067 --> 00:06:00.068 position:50% align:center
So? What's up?

00:06:00.151 --> 00:06:01.319 position:50% align:center
