new act of ours.

00:06:21.339 --> 00:06:22.507 position:50% align:center
[BOTH]
Mm.

00:06:22.590 --> 00:06:23.675 position:50% align:center
We'll do it!

00:06:23.758 --> 00:06:26.511 position:50% align:center
