You will? The only thing is--

00:06:26.594 --> 00:06:29.389 position:50% align:center
[MAFUYU]
We've gotta call Rin and Nayuta!

00:06:31.349 --> 00:06:33.685 position:50% align:center
And since you needed some
help to fill in the time

00:06:33.768 --> 00:06:35.437 position:50% align:center
