again with that air band thing?

00:08:04.067 --> 00:08:07.070 position:50% align:center
Honestly, Mafuyu.
Forget feeling down!

00:08:07.153 --> 00:08:09.614 position:50% align:center
You're practically
subterranean with negativity!

00:08:09.698 --> 00:08:12.742 position:50% align:center
But you know, the four of you
really saved us today,

00:08:12.826 --> 00:08:15.495 position:50% align:center
