Tokonatsu and RDeco.

00:08:25.505 --> 00:08:28.717 position:50% align:center
We'll be sure to give
you a proper invite!

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:30.385 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Mm!

00:08:36.349 --> 00:08:39.811 position:50% align:center
[MAFUYU groans]
The air band killed,

00:08:39.894 --> 00:08:42.731 position:50% align:center
