00:08:42.814 --> 00:08:44.399 position:50% align:center
[RIN]
You're still on that?

00:08:44.482 --> 00:08:46.109 position:50% align:center
Changing the mood
with a one-off gag

00:08:46.192 --> 00:08:48.778 position:50% align:center
