that isn't surprising.

00:08:48.862 --> 00:08:50.655 position:50% align:center
You have to set it up
better than that.

00:08:50.739 --> 00:08:53.783 position:50% align:center
Exactly. Just think about
how the crowd was earlier;

00:08:53.867 --> 00:08:56.536 position:50% align:center
we had them all pumped up
with that air band act of ours.

00:08:56.619 --> 00:08:59.539 position:50% align:center
hen you went and shoved that
gag in from out of nowhere.

00:08:59.622 --> 00:09:00.915 position:50% align:center
Read the atmosphere.

00:09:00.999 --> 00:09:03.418 position:50% align:center
It wasn't a light read. [laughs]

00:09:03.501 --> 00:09:05.503 position:50% align:center
I think that the audience
didn't really know how

00:09:05.587 --> 00:09:07.422 position:50% align:center
to react to that sudden
shift in tone.

00:09:07.505 --> 00:09:08.923 position:50% align:center
[MAFUYU]
Hmm.

00:09:09.007 --> 00:09:11.426 position:50% align:center
So, if we were talking desserts
you wouldn't want to have

00:09:11.509 --> 00:09:14.512 position:50% align:center
